0ad26da6.jpg\\\\\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片24.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"571\\\\\" height=\\\\\"387\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/ee01783b61389dbb4ff7a2320a7afccf.jpg\\\\\" />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''微软雅黑\\\\''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''微软雅黑\\\\''; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p\\\\\" style=\\\\\"padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p\\\\\" style=\\\\\"padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(0,0,255); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">http://www.hudsonhome.cn</span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment--></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('205','8','','1','0','0','0','','','','<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 你也想拥有一间舒适的房子吧，闯过了九九八十一难终于拿到了房子钥匙，但又立刻面临了一个问题，房子该怎么装修呢，毕竟装修好了就不能轻易变动，当然如果你有多余的金钱的话就另当别论了。（小提醒：文中有个别图非哈德逊产品，仅仅作为参考）</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp;哈德逊家居今天跟大家给大家介绍一下时下大多数人都细化的小清新装修风格。小清新风格是指清新唯美、随意创作风格。小清新秉承淡雅、自然、朴实、超脱、静谧的特点而存在着。这种风格特别是被80、90后追随着。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">小清新的颜色</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp;小清新的装修风格在颜色方面会比较偏向于比较淡的颜色，例如月白色、浅青色、浅草绿、淡黄等淡色系的颜色。淡颜色的风格给家营造一种清爽、放松的氛围，能够给已经工作了一天的心一个卸下战衣的休憩之所。淡色系的颜色能让你感受到慢节奏的生活气息，而不是匆匆走过的岁月。这也是很多年轻一代喜欢小清新的原因。下面贴图可以作为小清新颜色的选择推荐。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片25.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"600\\\\\" height=\\\\\"391\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/cea9d411dfbe4dcaafe77c43de0ae0de.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片26.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"599\\\\\" height=\\\\\"368\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/f7a491b419569863f244e0918cc4603a.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片27.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"594\\\\\" height=\\\\\"343\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/96d41ff464eb84d441483d2c65b1f915.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 颜色也不一定是这三种，重点是淡色系，看起来没有那么鲜明例如红色。那些比较深颜色的家居作为淡色系中的一点点缀会好看一点，万绿丛中一点红会让绿更加生动活泼。选定好装修的颜色后，我们从客厅开始一个个的为你简单的介绍小清新家具的装修分析。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">客厅</span></strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 客厅占据了一个家最大的空间，打开门最先看到的是客厅，接待亲戚朋友的也是客厅，所以客厅就像是人的脸面，暴露在外面给人以印象。客厅小清新的装饰一般只选定一种颜色，然后在家具等装饰上混进一点其他的颜色作为点缀号好一点，如果颜色太杂整体看起来会眼花缭乱扰人心境。而且客厅看起来应该大气简洁，不太适合杂乱的风格。客厅装修首先要解决分区问题。如果家人看电视的时间非常多，那么就可以视听柜为客厅中心，来确定沙发的位置和走向；如果不常看电视，客人又多，则完全可以会客区做为客厅的中心。 </span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">　</span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;客厅的地砖需要显得大气但又不失温馨、小清新。客厅地砖哈德逊家居推荐您选择选用地中海仿古风格。哈德逊地中海仿古地砖，颜色有巧克力色、米白色这两种淡色系颜色，给人一种沉稳、淡雅、清新的感觉。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">　　<img alt=\\\\\"图片28.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"500\\\\\" height=\\\\\"504\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/df53c84697ce4fde168ac2ed3a3f1a4f.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果你觉得地板仅仅用仿古砖会显得单调的话，可以选择文化墙作为调适，文化墙会个客厅带来书香气息，让你的客厅也显得有气质，给来访者眼前一亮的感觉。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片29.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"600\\\\\" height=\\\\\"396\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/4dc6676d2d25e2323a537a19fe20cfe6.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果你在地砖上面加入地毯的话，地砖也可以选择哈德逊奢华时尚的微晶石。参照图如下：</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">　　<img alt=\\\\\"图片30.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"392\\\\\" height=\\\\\"395\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/0af4422c9284db3331f5055e163feb91.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片31.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"506\\\\\" height=\\\\\"390\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/9be73743537a39148b9d2f2392a65256.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 调好地砖后我们来看看选择怎么样的家具吧，客厅的家居推荐一套沙发，外加一两张小清新风格的凳子。譬如下图这些。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">　　<img alt=\\\\\"图片32.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"503\\\\\" height=\\\\\"388\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/79ac9fc306902fd461a1af988e999007.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 桌子小清新风格可以参考下面一些款式：</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">　　　<img alt=\\\\\"图片33.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"400\\\\\" height=\\\\\"308\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/51538b1595a42bd0a161aeaba0414e7e.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片34.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"506\\\\\" height=\\\\\"390\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/c30805d8e55e90d9a6cd2fff329bcda2.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 客厅装修整体效果参考：</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片35.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"600\\\\\" height=\\\\\"389\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/0dabeeee2ec9798456bf9f476ca5ce23.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"图片36.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"600\\\\\" height=\\\\\"403\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/xwzx/qyxw/2014-06-05/9fab014457e9f04d6ed1c8225219236b.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 哈德逊小编一下子无法说清楚整个家的小清新装修风格，先讲到客厅吧，晚点再更新卧室的小清新装修风格推荐。</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p\\\\\" style=\\\\\"padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">文章来源：哈德逊瓷砖编辑原创</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p\\\\\" style=\\\\\"padding-bottom: 0pt; line-height: 18pt; margin-top: 0pt; padding-left: 0pt; padding-right: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-family: 宋体; letter-spacing: 0pt; color: rgb(102,102,102); font-size: 10.5pt; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt\\\\\">转载请注明出处</span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/\\\\\"><span 